comment: Gortat (WAS) sets the screen on Harris (BKN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Beal (WAS) hops consecutively on the same foot upon ending his dribble.
Porter (WAS) does not obtain a legal guarding position at the time of the contact with Lopez (BKN).
Lopez (BKN) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Kilpatrick (BKN) and Beal (WAS) briefly engage and separate.
Morris (WAS) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Kilpatrick (BKN) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Beal (WAS) cleanly strips the ball from Harris (BKN).
Bogdanovic (BKN) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
Hollis-Jefferson (BKN) commits a take foul on Wall (WAS).
